Don't use any SmartMechanisms.
I think they're inflexible and generally after using them I don't really like them.

Use SmartMotorControllers, they're good and I like them.

Grintake: Two NEOs, one on the pivot, one on the intake.

Indexer: Two NEOs, one on main, one on kicker. Also a beambreak to detect when main should run.

HoodedShooter: Three NEOs, one on hood, two on the flywheel, one flywheel motor following the other.